imdb.title: Misguided
plot: _Misguided_ (qv) is an improvised comedy television show where four characters are 'misguided' by a live studio audience. The characters and storylines progress every episode and all four storylines come together at the end of the season.::Phillip McKechnie

Join Colonel Hans as he tries to destroy his nemesis General Lucien; Grandma Elise who wants to attend the wedding of her estranged grandson; George Hobart as he desperately tries to find a cure for his mother's disease; and Penelope Bridgebank-Bankman as she tries to create the greatest fashion collection of all time! What will happen on our characters' journeys? Watch _Misguided_ (qv) to find out!::Phillip McKechnie

Season 2 - Join Felix Ra Sha as he tries to avenge the death of his parents; socially awkward Bev Fitzpatrick as she tries to win a Beauty Pageant; Edward Von Huxtable who wants to find a long lost treasure his grandfather could never find; and Val Charleston-Blake on her journey to become a fully-fledged card carrying psychic!::Phillip McKechnie
